About us

Who we are

Our Mission

Restoration of Life Transitional Homes is a faithbased nonprofit in Anna, Texas. We provide shortterm housing and wraparound care for individuals and families working toward stability, sobriety, and selfsufficiency.

Our team offers coaching, goal setting, and connections to jobs, benefits, and longterm housing resourcesbecause a safe place is only the beginning.

Who we serve

  • Individuals and parents with children seeking stable housing
  • Neighbors exiting crisis, shelters, or unsafe situations
  • Those committed to a structured, supportive environment

We welcome everyone with dignityno one walks alone.
